  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300140153_29_7336-7422",
      "chapterUid": 29,
      "range": "7336-7422",
      "markText": "我也许是个白痴，但大多数时候，无论怎样，我都会尽力做对的事——梦想终归是梦想，不是吗？因此，无论发生了什么其他的事，我都在想：我总可以回顾过去，说至少我这一生没有碌碌无为。",
      "totalCount": 896,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300140153&chapterUid=29&rangeStart=7336&rangeEnd=7422",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f1232e60813ab9d3fg01378c?chapterUid=29&rangeStart=7336&rangeEnd=7422"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300140153_7_1601-1631",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "1601-1631",
      "markText": "这简直就是天堂般的生活，直到我发现珍妮·柯伦和班卓琴手睡觉。",
      "totalCount": 408,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300140153&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1601&rangeEnd=1631",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f1232e60813ab9d3fg01378c?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1601&rangeEnd=1631"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300140153_12_1562-1611",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "1562-1611",
      "markText": "他不时回头看我，我就拍打翅膀。大约过了一个钟头，他停了车，我看向窗外，该死，他竟然把我拉到了机场！",
      "totalCount": 400,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300140153&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=1562&rangeEnd=1611",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f1232e60813ab9d3fg01378c?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=1562&rangeEnd=1611"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300140153_12_2571-2588",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "2571-2588",
      "markText": "有时候，不能让对的事挡住你的去路。",
      "totalCount": 352,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300140153&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=2571&rangeEnd=2588",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f1232e60813ab9d3fg01378c?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=2571&rangeEnd=2588"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300140153_12_906-958",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "906-958",
      "markText": "中国人用两根小棍子吃饭，几乎不可能把任何食物送进嘴里，结果很多食物掉到我身上。难怪在中国见不到几个胖子。",
      "totalCount": 351,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300140153&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=906&rangeEnd=958",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f1232e60813ab9d3fg01378c?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=906&rangeEnd=958"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300140153_4_3209-3233",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "3209-3233",
      "markText": "十六岁时，我身高六英尺六英寸，体重二百四十二磅。",
      "totalCount": 306,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300140153&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3209&rangeEnd=3233",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f1232e60813ab9d3fg01378c?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3209&rangeEnd=3233"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300140153_7_4914-4965",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "4914-4965",
      "markText": "该回到场上去了。所有人呐喊欢呼，但这副重担压在我肩上，我觉得有点不公平。可是，管他呢，有时候就是这样。",
      "totalCount": 288,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300140153&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=4914&rangeEnd=4965",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f1232e60813ab9d3fg01378c?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=4914&rangeEnd=4965"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300140153_4_5495-5508",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "5495-5508",
      "markText": "还有别的东西，但我不敢讲。",
      "totalCount": 280,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300140153&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5495&rangeEnd=5508",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f1232e60813ab9d3fg01378c?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5495&rangeEnd=5508"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300140153_6_5394-5480",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "5394-5480",
      "markText": "我摆弄了一会儿口琴，渐渐地，就吹得相当不错了，布巴兴奋到发疯，说从来没听过这么好听的音乐。天色已晚，布巴让我把口琴带走，我把口琴带回地下室，又吹了很久，直到困了，上床睡觉。",
      "totalCount": 272,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300140153&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=5394&rangeEnd=5480",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f1232e60813ab9d3fg01378c?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=5394&rangeEnd=5480"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300140153_4_433-446",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "433-446",
      "markText": "：当白痴可不像一盒巧克力。",
      "totalCount": 270,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300140153&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=433&rangeEnd=446",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f1232e60813ab9d3fg01378c?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=433&rangeEnd=446"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300140153_10_5632-5699",
